tool_description:
Real-time data, unofficial API skyscanner.com, query hotels, flights.
API searches and compares hotel and rental car options to help them find the best deal for their journey.

api_list.name: get-config
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sky-scanner3.p.rapidapi.com/get-config"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sky-scanner3.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
